profile:
Shutters to Suit your taste and budget
Whether you dream a modern contemporary look ... or a traditional classic one ... ShuttersDirect has beautiful Plantation Shutters that can give you the look you desire. 

Choose either water resistant Vinyl Shutters. Or choose painted or stained Hardwood Shutters. 

You can create the look you’re dreaming of ... while also increasing your home’s live-ability, curb appeal, and value. That’s sure to make you smile. And your windows will never look better! 



    

Shutters crafted to the finest quality 





Crafted right here in Canada. Plantation Shutters are the peak of posh for window coverings. 

Plantation Shutters ... also known as California Shutters and Oceanview Shutters ... are crafted-to- measure to your window’s exact size and design specifications. 

Adding custom crafted interior shutters will make such a big difference to the look of your home. 

Plus “Crafted in Canada” assures you of the finest in materials and fitment practices.
